---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="PyCon 2025 - Annual Python Conference" description="Join us for PyCon 2025, the annual Python conference bringing together developers, data scientists, and enthusiasts for talks, workshops, and networking.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <img src="/pycon-2025/assets/event-image-1.png" alt="PyCon 2025 Event Banner" class="hero-image" />
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>PyCon 2025</h1>
      <p>The Premier Annual Python Conference</p>
      <p>Bringing together developers, data scientists, and enthusiasts for talks, workshops, and networking.</p>
      <a href="#register" class="cta-button">Register Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about">
    <h2>About PyCon 2025</h2>
    <p>
      PyCon 2025 is the premier annual conference for the Python community. Whether you're a seasoned developer, a data scientist exploring new frontiers, or an enthusiast eager to learn, PyCon brings together the brightest minds in the Python ecosystem.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our conference features world-class talks from industry leaders, hands-on workshops covering cutting-edge topics, and unparalleled networking opportunities with fellow Python enthusiasts from around the globe.
    </p>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Expert Talks</h3>
        <p>Learn from industry leaders and core Python developers sharing insights on the latest trends, best practices, and innovations in the Python ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Hands-On Workshops</h3>
        <p>Participate in interactive workshops covering topics from web development and data science to machine learning and DevOps.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Networking</h3>
        <p>Connect with thousands of Python developers, data scientists, and enthusiasts. Build relationships that can shape your career.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Schedule Section -->
  <section id="schedule">
    <h2>Schedule</h2>
    <p>PyCon 2025 runs for three days packed with keynotes, talks, workshops, and social events.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Day 1: Keynotes & Opening</h3>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> May 16, 2025</p>
        <p>Join us for opening remarks and inspiring keynote presentations from Python community leaders. Meet fellow attendees at the welcome reception.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Day 2: Talks & Workshops</h3>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> May 17, 2025</p>
        <p>Dive deep into parallel tracks of technical talks and hands-on workshops. Choose from topics spanning web development, data science, DevOps, and more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Day 3: Advanced Topics & Closing</h3>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> May 18, 2025</p>
        <p>Explore advanced topics, attend lightning talks, and join us for the closing ceremony and networking dinner.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Venue Section -->
  <section id="venue">
    <h2>Venue</h2>
    <p>
      PyCon 2025 will be held at the Convention Center in Portland, Oregon, a world-class venue with state-of-the-art facilities designed to host our growing community.
    </p>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Location</h3>
        <p><strong>Portland Convention Center</strong></p>
        <p>777 NE Martin Luther King Jr. Blvd<br />Portland, OR 97232<br />United States</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Accessibility</h3>
        <p>The venue is fully accessible with wheelchair access, accessible restrooms, and accommodations for attendees with disabilities. ASL interpretation and live captioning will be provided.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Getting There</h3>
        <p>Conveniently located near public transportation. Free parking available for registered attendees. Shuttle service from major hotels.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Register Section -->
  <section id="register">
    <h2>Register</h2>
    <p>
      Secure your spot at PyCon 2025 today! Early bird tickets are available at a special rate until April 30, 2025.
    </p>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Early Bird</h3>
        <p><strong>$199</strong></p>
        <p>Available until April 30, 2025</p>
        <p>Includes all three days of talks, workshops, meals, and networking events.</p>
        <button class="cta-button" onclick="alert('Registration coming soon!')" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 1rem;">Register Early Bird</button>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Regular</h3>
        <p><strong>$299</strong></p>
        <p>Available May 1 - May 15, 2025</p>
        <p>Includes all three days of talks, workshops, meals, and networking events.</p>
        <button class="cta-button" onclick="alert('Registration coming soon!')" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 1rem;">Register</button>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Student</h3>
        <p><strong>$99</strong></p>
        <p>Valid student ID required</p>
        <p>Includes all three days of talks, workshops, meals, and networking events.</p>
        <button class="cta-button" onclick="alert('Registration coming soon!')" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 1rem;">Register as Student</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>